384
00:44:00,640 --> 00:44:03,518
Gentlemen, let us make our peace
over a bottle.

385
00:44:03,640 --> 00:44:07,997
Sir, it is no slight matter for a man
of my character to be buffeted by a boy

386
00:44:08,120 --> 00:44:10,554
