420
00:46:08,480 --> 00:46:10,436
Good night, Sister.

421
00:46:15,160 --> 00:46:16,798
Brother!

422
00:46:20,480 --> 00:46:22,232
Brother!

423
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:27,914
Brother!

424
00:46:28,040 --> 00:46:29,837
Oh, stop!

425
00:46:31,080 --> 00:46:32,957
Brother!

426
00:46:38,200 --> 00:46:43,832
Brother, have you not noticed something
very extraordinary about Sophie lately?

427
00:46:43,960 --> 00:46:47,475
Tell me, then. You know I love that girl
more than my own soul.

428
00:46:47,600 --> 00:46:52,469
Well, unless I am deceived,
my niece is desperately in love.

429
00:46:53,120 --> 00:46:55,111
In love?

430
00:46:55,240 --> 00:46:57,708
In love?! Without my consent?!

431
00:46:58,840 --> 00:47:00,956
I'll disinherit her!

432
00:47:02,560 --> 00:47:06,030
I'll cast her out-of-doors
stark naked without a farthing!

433
00:47:06,160 --> 00:47:07,309
Where is she?

434
00:47:07,440 --> 00:47:11,592
Supposing she should have fixed on
the very person you would have wished?

435
00:47:11,720 --> 00:47:15,838
No. No! She can love whom she pleases,
but she'll marry the man I choose!

436
00:47:15,960 --> 00:47:19,270
<i>But she has fixed on the very person
you would have wished!</i>

437
00:47:20,960 --> 00:47:23,110
- What?
- What think you of Mr Blifil?

438
00:47:24,640 --> 00:47:27,837
- Young Blifil?
- Well, who else could there be?

439
00:47:27,960 --> 00:47:32,397
